window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I married a space elf, but now a space demon is after me.</b></p> <p>After making a big family with the most influential species in the galaxy, life was pretty sweet. I had a powerful ship, powerful allies, and all the variety a man could ever ask for.</p> <p>But when the beings responsible for the fertility-killing mutagen I was born to counter re-emerge, it’s up to me to step up and do what I do best.</p> <p>And that includes boldly loving what no man has loved before.</p>"; 
